      "duration": "",
      "published_date": "",
      "apple_rating": 0,
      "chunk_text": "這是因爲歷史上的經濟思想家通常都來自社會中最優越的羣體嗎?",
      "embedding": [],
      "language": "zh",
      "created_at": "2025-07-10T14:46:53.013658",
